</style><p>其中，Naraka 于 3 月 31 日参加了由 Shishirobotan (Hololive) 赞助的街头霸王 6 锦标赛项目“Shishakuhai”。就像与天音彼方等 Hololive Productions 的艺人合作过的天宫心一样，她也曾与其他公司的艺人合作过项目。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[街头霸王6] #狮尺煞制作！让我们一起欣赏吧！" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/K42hcmLuptc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p>此外，还曝出芦木先生通过自己的广播对夏色祭（Hololive）、紫崎紫苑（同上）、音玉（青桐高中）等人进行了性骚扰。志愿者们纷纷列出了自己过去的所作所为。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="完整聊天：CR杯、Vtuber、漫画" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SJ1D4y2y8io?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><p>这次，如果确认足木先生不仅是天宫心的版主，而且还是二十三寺旗下多个人才的版主，那么他就真正成为了<em>雨宫心的版主，进一步成为版主和利益相关者的可能性</em>增加。 <span style="text-decoration: underline;">ANYCOLOR（虹彩）相关人员对Cover Co., Ltd.（Hololive Productions）、Brave Group等其他公司的艺人进行诽谤、发表不当评论和评论，且至今未道歉。可以断定没有采取此类行动</span>。</p><p> 2022年12月5日，水成星町所属Hololive Production运营的Cover Co., Ltd.和《Nijisanji》运营的ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-cover-corp-and-nijisanji-anycolor-inc-have-joined-forces-to-fight-slander-and-a-joint-statement-was-also-issued/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="关于反诽谤措施的联合声明的公告">发表了关于打击诽谤和诽谤措施的联合声明。</a>对于ANYCOLOR Inc.（Nijisanji）的官员对Cover Inc.（Hololive Productions）的诽谤行为，不能<a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-cover-corp-and-nijisanji-anycolor-inc-have-joined-forces-to-fight-slander-and-a-joint-statement-was-also-issued/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="关于反诽谤措施的联合声明的公告">说</a><strong>两家公司的联合声明实际上已经成为一个空壳，你不会明白的</strong>。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="MPwa3asFlU"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/slanderer-against-hoshimachi-suisei-admitted-i-am-nijisanji-moderator-and-relation/">水星星町的诽谤者承认，“我是《虹山寺》的版主，与它有关。”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Suisei Hoshimachi 的诽谤者承认，‘我是 Nijisanji 的版主和附属机构。’” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/slanderer-against-hoshimachi-suisei-admitted-i-am-nijisanji-moderator-and-relation/embed/#?secret=VnIqQdx8GL#?secret=MPwa3asFlU" data-secret="MPwa3asFlU" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="6y0rvnhS8l"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/is-the-slanderer-of-hoshimachi-suisei-a-moderator-of-nijisanji-vtuber-amamiya-kokoro/">星町水成的诽谤者已成为二十三寺旗下 VTuber 雨宫心的可能版主。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“水星星町的诽谤者：出现了成为二十三寺的VTuber天宫心的版主的可能性” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/is-the-slanderer-of-hoshimachi-suisei-a-moderator-of-nijisanji-vtuber-amamiya-kokoro/embed/#?secret=ElN7Il1rCq#?secret=6y0rvnhS8l" data-secret="6y0rvnhS8l" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p><strong>再次强调，请您务必不仅查看本文，还请查看人才本人、所在机构、团体、公司提供的主要信息。如果您遇到恶意信息或诽谤，请通过以下方式与我们联系。谢谢感谢您让我们知道。</strong></p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow"><p><a href="https://cover-corp.com/report/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">如果您发现“Hololive Productions”所属人员有任何诽谤或侵犯版权的行为，请在此处与我们联系。</a></p><cite>封面有限公司</cite></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow"><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5CwaMl1eIgY8h02uZw7u8A" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">水成频道</a>/<a href="https://twitter.com/suisei_hosimati" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">水成星町<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2604.png" alt="☄" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Hololive 第 0 代</a>/ <a href="https://hololive.hololivepro.com/talents/hoshimachi-suisei/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">星町水成</a></p><cite>YouTube / X（推特）/ Hololive Production</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="SGn67j63OA"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/slanderer-against-hololive-hoshimachi-suisei-also-moderator-of-other-nijisanji-vtuber-besides-amamiya-kokoro/">诽谤hololive 星町水成，除了雨宫心之外，也是《NIJISANJI》其他VTuber 的版主？</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“诽谤hololive星町翠星，除了雨宫心之外，也是二十三寺VTuber的版主？” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/slanderer-against-hololive-hoshimachi-suisei-also-moderator-of-other-nijisanji-vtuber-besides-amamiya-kokoro/embed/#?secret=IYLszIJ9Fc#?secret=SGn67j63OA" data-secret="SGn67j63OA" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/slanderer-against-hololive-hoshimachi-suisei-also-moderator-of-other-nijisanji-vtuber-besides-amamiya-kokoro/">诽谤hololive/星町水生的帖子除了雨宫心之外，他还负责二十三寺VTuber的版主吗？</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/slanderer-against-hololive-hoshimachi-